refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 booloci_fetch
 resourcestatement



 Fetches the next row (for SELECT statements) into the internal
 result-buffer.

&oci.datatypes;

&reftitle.parameters;




   statement



     A valid OCI statement identifier.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Returns &true; on success or &false; if there are no more rows in the
 statement.
